      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for its next adventure? This car is in really nice shape and drives like a total dream! It\u2019s been my trusty companion for daily commutes and weekend getaways, and it's still got so much life left in it. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it feels on the road!",
