    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated powerplant delivers linear torque through individual throttle bodies, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement and a recently serviced variable M-differential. Suspension kinematics are preserved with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor patina consistent with its driver-focused history, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, ensuring timing precision across the 8,000 RPM range. A purist\u2019s spec for those valuing drivetrain integrity and analog feedback.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
