    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though I want to be fully transparent about a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the leather seats remain supple, showing only light softening on the driver-side bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is sound. It features a complete service history with a recent oil change, fresh brake pads, and a set of premium tires with significant tread remaining. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are crisp and certain. This is a reliable, high-quality driver\u2019s car that needs nothing but a new owner. Includes two sets of keys and all original manuals.",
